Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:02.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:04.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the start of Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:06.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gatherall\nthe shards of the Sacred Jewel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'll destroy Naraku with\nmy Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's older brother, Sesshomaru,\ndetested humans so much,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:15.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet a young mortal girl\nnow accompanies him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:18.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His vassal Jaken is caught between them\nand they're quite a trio!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:20.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:22.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:24.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In pursuit of Naraku\nwho had disappeared,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:06.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we were headed northeast in the\ndirection of the ox-tiger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:09.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the same time, Inuyasha's\nolder brother, Sesshomaru,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}was also looking for Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:35.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,May I go and look\nfor something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:37.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quiet, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aforest like this will have\nnothing foryou to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just bear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:42.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I'll be real quick!\N- That girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:51.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let herbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why'd you eat it all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:02.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This was the last\nbag of garlic-flavored chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's one bag ortwo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:11.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to give it\nto Jinenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, you nevereat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:16.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ljust took one piece...\nand I couldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This Jinenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Kirara collapsed from\NNaraku's toxic poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was Jinenji who gave\nus the antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:37.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're nearhis village,\nso I thought we could stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But someone ate his present!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quitgoing on about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, isn't Jinenji also\na half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:48.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, but he's so gentle\nand nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unlike Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:54.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well! There's no present forhim.\NSo let's just keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:04:00.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If there's an antidote to the miasma,\nwe should stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to thank him for\nsaving Kirara, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let's all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha can do as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's so heartless!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brilliant! You are the one and only\NLord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so dashing, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those are poisonous Saimyosho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He left behind\nsome annoying vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There should be a hive nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll look forit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!\NMasterJaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There! The hive of the poison insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:34.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get a taste of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Staff ofTwo Heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Persistent pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin! Keep yourhead down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must protect Rin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise, who knows what\NLord Sesshomaru will say!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}MasterJaken...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:02.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saved me, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:26.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:32.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterJaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I pursue them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take the stingers out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:52.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you get them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The toxic poisons have\nentered my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I don't do something,\NI may die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,F-Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm notgoing to die\nforyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm dying for Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterJaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there some way\nto get rid of the poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay, Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:35.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have been happy traveling\nthe land with Lord Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:41.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if I should die here,\NI have no regrets in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterJaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell Lord Sesshomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:53.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that I will be praying for\nhis well-being...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,from my grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterJaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to see\nyou die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:07.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:12.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then maybe I'll ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}MasterJaken... don't die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:33.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To the east of here is an herb farm\nknown as Jinenji's Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go there and get the berries
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,of the {\i1}sennensou{\i0}\N"thousand-yearflower."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The berries of\nthe "thousand-yearflower"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:47.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you truly want to save me,\nyou must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before the sun sets, I must\nswallow the berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,else the toxic poison will have\nspread throughout my body
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I shall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will return before the sun sets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promise!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-Uun! Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... are you sure it's\nthis way, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:19.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, Inuyasha?\NIt WAS this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:27.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I didn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:30.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you still sulking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry for being rude earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man! She didn't even mean it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's poisonous insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Couldn't ask for better luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:01.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome... do you sense\nany Sacred Jewel shards nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No... not nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And no demon puppets either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:11.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then perhaps those insects are\nheading back to Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:14.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we follow them\ninstead of killing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll discover Naraku's whereabouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Hey! They're falling!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are they dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you kill them...\nthe Saimyosho?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saimyosho?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:49.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean these poison insects?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So short-sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:52.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:56.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I've lost my lead\nto finding Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lemme make one thing clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These bugs just dropped dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm becoming quite tired\nof yourexcuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:07.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd make excuses to you!\NI'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay outta this, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He doesn't understand words!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:18.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling very\nmagnanimous today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won'tgo easy on you\nlike before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:26.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And don't come crying to\nme later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're always at\nodds with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-Un, wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An herbal garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:13.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! A witch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:19.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:23.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I want to see Jinenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jinenji isn't seeing anyone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:27.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're here, aren't you, Jinenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please hearme out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please give me some\n{\i1}sennensouberries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's someone who's been\npoisoned and he might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's very regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have any\n{\i1}sennensouberries{\i0} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why won't you come out\nfrom underthe covers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:57.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just a little girl,\nso you won't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:00.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Jinenji is\na half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:06.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once in a while, he takes on\nthe human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's such a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:13.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he doesn't want anyone\nto see his human self.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then please tell me where\NI can find the berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sennensouberries{\i0} are used as\nan antidote by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you trying to save a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:25.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:28.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you smitten with this demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Smitten?\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so young!\NI underestimated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was like you once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must save MasterJaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:46.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This girl resembles Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, thatgirl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}sennensou{\i0} grows in the ravine\nof the mountain out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are lots of demons and beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's impossible for a human\nto go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When it's dark,\NI'll return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So can you wait until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:16.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me what kind of plant it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:25.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really... you're just like Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:31.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:40.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... don't... want to die... alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:56.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-Un! There!\NThat's the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:05.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's my win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you prepared, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't care about my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:24.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:25.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to know where Naraku is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then go in the direction of\nthe ox-tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:34.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We heard that Naraku's aura\nwent in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stu... - ! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the direction of the ox-tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You survived this one, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you go after Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:01.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, A-Un!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sennensouberries...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Thousand-yearflower" berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:39.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:09.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, A-Un!\NKeep them at bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to get the berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Sesshomaru...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:41.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:51.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pa... Ma... Brother...\NThey all died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want anyone else\nto die...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:03.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to see anyone die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}MasterJaken...\NPlease don't die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:35.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't anyone die... anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:12.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The poison is spreading...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:17.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahh... the sun is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin didn't make it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:28.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh... my vision is blurring...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? An illusion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:35.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,L-Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterJaken, don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Alittle girl came by?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:07.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm worried if she was able\nto get the {\i1}sennensou{\i0} berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think she did okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was just like you, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:20.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... she's probably much\nstrongerthan me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:24.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like Kagome, she warmed your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:27.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She must have a big, kind heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:34.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jinenji... please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Jinenji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you misunderstand,\nso lemme tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:43.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's heart is pretty small.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'd I tell ya, Jinenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:53.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See how small herheart is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! Sit! Sit! Sit! Sit! Sit! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Second that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:11.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:16.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Master Jaken?\NYou're cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:21.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or did I... die again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:26.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silly fool! Lord Sesshomaru\nbrought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:33.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop giving him so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:36.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:40.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohhh... But MasterJaken,\NI'm so glad foryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:43.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh... stop, Rin!\NGet away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:44.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the direction of the ox-tiger...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:53.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:02.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're all together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:47.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do, Kagome?\NKirara is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.60,0:23:49.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe she went for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:51.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara seemed fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:53.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this is the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:56.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a reason why\nshe can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:58.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm getting so worried\nthe more I think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:02.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could she have run away\nbecause of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Kirara Come Home!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.08,0:24:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, don't leave like this!
